## Implementation
- Use Expo's optimized Image component or react-native-fast-image
- Specify width and height for all images to prevent layout shifts instead of using NativeWind's w- or h- classes
- Use appropriate resizeMode (cover, contain, etc.)
- Implement progressive loading for large images

## Performance
- Compress and optimize images before bundling
- Use WebP format when possible for better compression
- Implement proper caching strategies for remote images
- Consider lazy loading for offscreen images
